{"tid":555532,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"其實TVB並唔垃圾 垃圾既係觀眾","createTime":"2018-02-09T14:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T18:11:22.000Z","uid":68626,"like":9,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a38e9072739ef746e86bb22de5643ea51efdf7b6","tid":555532,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T14:05:52.000Z","msg":"呢個世界有供有求<br />\n你估TVB唔想拍下D題材陰暗/寫真既片咩<br />\n屌那星個班師奶 斬下手手腳腳已經投訴又盛<br />\n基本上個題材/路線/結局 已經一早注定左<br />\n同比人渣住個春袋無分別<br />\nTVB唔係無能力拍好劇 係唔想拍咋<br />\n有咩觀眾咪有咩電視睇囉<br />\n你地班連登仔 日日係到話咩幾耐幾耐無睇TVB<br />\n你地咪唔撚好睇 咪得番班師奶睇<br />\n咪拍番相應題材囉 仲想點撚樣呀<br />\n唔通你預放學ICU有床戲比你睇咩?"},{"pid":"d11b4abbee0112f909ff02f65d21d1d3da9f9baf","tid":555532,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T14:22:23.000Z","msg":"我愛溏心風暴之家好月圓"},{"pid":"91be2664a87ab6231fa12511d3fc02f76dd1e0d2","tid":555532,"uid":19275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"真係無睇好耐，見到咁多post講就覺得好礙眼"},{"pid":"782e2fc1385bf4122df23fac19e77cccefbd53b5","tid":555532,"uid":14265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"在座各位都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27cfc996f84b95d86fd94a5469529bad432f3a0","tid":555532,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:26:31.000Z","msg":"我打算開始狙擊你"},{"pid":"d03068c19c38749fbf683332a1aaeffc9699be9b","tid":555532,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T18:11:22.000Z","msg":"幾時投訴新聞報道命案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}